== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 18 Kanama 1988 iMbombela, Mpumalanga, <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=17781</ref> Afurika y'Epfo aho yakuriye mu nzu ya nyirakuru. Yarangije impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu buhanzi yakuye muri kaminuza yâ€™ikoranabuhanga ya Tshwane, Pretoria kabuhariwe mu ikinamico. <ref name="youthvillage">https://www.youthvillage.co.za/2016/08/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-skeem-saams-nickolas-nkuna/</ref> Hanyuma yagiye muri Ball State University, Indiana muri Amerika, yiga gukina. 

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina mumyaka ya kaminuza, aho yakinnye mumikino myinshi yikinamico nka ''Parade'', ''Inzozi Zabakobwa'', ''Shaka Zulu'', ''Sophiatown'', ''Oliver Twist'', ''Gukodesha'', na ''Assassins'' . <ref>https://www.bona.co.za/a-victorious-truth-with-nicholas-nkuna/</ref> Yakinnye kandi mu makinamico nka Simba mu ikinamico yitwa Yanakinnye mu ikinamico ''Ntare King'' aho yazengurutse Irlande n'Ubwongereza akina.  Ku myaka 22, Nkuna abaye umukinnyi wa kabiri wa Afurika wakinnye mu ikinamico izwi cyane ya ''Phantom ya Opera'' . 

Muri 2015, yerekeje kuri televiziyo, ''Skeem Saam'', abinyujije kuri agent, biba televiziyo ye ya mbere. Muri serial, yakinnye nka 'Sakhile'. Muri 2017, yafashe ikiruhuko cy'imyaka 3, aho yongeye kwerekeza mu Kwakira 2020. <ref>https://iharare.com/nicholas-nkuna-is-back-on-skeem-saam/</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, yitabiriye urukurikirane rw'amarushanwa yo gukina BET, ''Top Actor Africa'' . Mu marushanwa, yagaragaye nkuwakabiri. Nyuma yaje kugaragara muri opera yisabune ''Roer Jou Voete'' akina nka 'Shakes Mbebe' mu mpera za 2015.  Muri 2016, yagaragaye muri serial ''Keeping Score'', kandi yagize uruhare ruto nkumukinnyi wa congo 'Issac'. Muri uwo mwaka, yatumiriwe kugira uruhare mu bashyitsi kuri serial izwi cyane ya ''Rhythm City'' . 

Kuva muri 2017, akina uruhare ruzwi cyane 'Fikani Chauke' murukurikirane ''7de Laan'' . <ref name="youthvillage" /> Yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza kurusha abandi muri Afurika y'Epfo Broadway Awards 2016 kubera uruhare rwe 'Mingus' mu ikinamico ''Sophiatown'' . Hanyuma yakinnye muri serie ''Erfsondes'' nka 'Ubwisanzure'. Usibye televiziyo, yanakinnye muri filime, ''Love by Chance'' and ''Meet the Radebes.'' 

Usibye gukina, ni n'umuririmbyi wamamaye. Indirimbo ebyiri mu ndirimbo zagaragaye muri filime yakinnye na Khanyi Mbau "Icyumba gitukura" naho indirimbo ye Thando igaragara kuri Meet the RAdebes.   Nicholas uzwi kandi ku izina rya Nicksoul afite igihembo cy'umuziki wo muri Afurika y'Epfo kubera alubumu ye ya mbere / r & b yise Therapy yasohotse muri 2018.

